NAME

  Latin9 - Source code filter to escape Latin-9 script

SYNOPSIS

  use Latin9;

DESCRIPTION

  The Latin9 software provides character oriented Perl scripting
  environment in Latin-9 by easy installation and easy usage.

  - Character oriented regular expression
  - Byte oriented built-in functions
      and
  - Character oriented subroutines
  - Byte oriented regular expression on /b modifier

INSTALLATION

  Just copy Latin9.pm and Elatin9.pm to your @INC directory.
  for example, to C:\Perl\site\lib

SUBROUTINES

  Latin9::length(charstring)
  Latin9::substr(charstring, charpos, charlen)
  etc

SEE ALSO

  http://search.cpan.org/~ina/

